:::
:::

## Ingredients

- [ ] 1/4 cup kernels
- [ ] ~1 Tbsp butter
- [ ] ~1 tsp cinnamon
- [ ] ~2 tsp sugar

## Recipe

1. Place in popper and cook for 2:20 in our 900 watt microwave
1. Microwave the butter until softened then mix with the popcorn. Coat with the cinnamon and sugar

## Notes

1. Measurements are all estimates
